        </item>
        <item>
            <title>智能家居品牌 IMOU 與 Winco 合作，提供安全防盜及智能家居產品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/imou-winco/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=imou-winco</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/imou-winco/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:52:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1196962</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Winco (Pacific) Limited 榮幸宣佈成為智能家居產品品牌 IMOU (樂橙) 的指定授權代理。IMOU 圍繞安防、互聯、機器人和照明系統四大方面推出不同智能家居產品，其中以網路攝影機，智能門鎖等安防產品最受歡迎，為每位使用者提供更簡單、安全的智能生活。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/PressRelease_Photo2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2><strong>IMOU Rex 2D/3D </strong><strong>室內網路攝影機系列，全景及定點巡航指定位置提供最佳保護</strong></h2><p>Rex2D/3D 是 IMOU 室內攝影機的系列之一，Rex 2D 提供全日錄影、動態偵測、一鍵鏡頭遮蔽或警報聲保護等等。Rex 2D 特別提供觀看影片密碼解鎖功能，為用家進一步加強私隱保護。Rex 2D 和 Rex 3D 擁有其他室內攝影機系列沒有的全景及定點巡航功能，能夠全方位巡視你所指定的位置，令你即使出門也能隨時掌握家中情況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rex2D3D_lifestyle-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Rex 3D 除了擁有上述基本功能以外，更搭配了 IMOU 最新的 IMOU SENSE 人工智能技術，其 AI 偵測功能比一般鏡頭高達 50% 的準確度，而且裝置也能夠辨認到寵物和人體，若你想隨時知道小孩或寵物的近況，那 Rex 3D 就會是你的最佳選擇。Rex 3D 也是唯一提供自訂警報音功能的室內鏡頭型號。假若你希望使用預設警報音以外的音效，也可以錄製一個屬於你的警報音去做保障。</p><p><strong> </strong></p><h2><strong>IMOU Knight 8MP </strong><strong>最高清戶外鏡頭，特有越線偵測功能，為家門提供最全面防護</strong></h2><p>Knight 8MP 作為 IMOU 的超高清室外鏡頭，其 8MP 解像度亦可稱為 4K，即水平方向顯示內容達到或大約 4096 像素。Knight 擁有車輛偵測功能，而且有 IMOU 產品中獨特的越線偵測功能，讓使用者能夠在系統上自訂線條，當有人越過線條時就會發出警報。使用者可以在家門前畫上線條，以作為自己家門外的一道防線。除此以外 Knight 8MP 也是市面上少數支援 WiFi 6 的無線網絡鏡頭，令你可以更快更流暢觀看門前狀況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-1273x900.jpg 1273w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-768x543.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-1536x1086.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Knight48MP_lifestyle-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><strong> </strong></p><h2><strong>DB60 Kit </strong><strong>視像門鈴及智能響鈴套裝，簡單方便，提升智慧生活</strong></h2><p>DB60 Kit 是將安全視像監控和智能門鈴合二為一的產品，套裝包含智能無線視像門鈴（DB60）和智能響鈴（DS21）。除了提供一般的錄影功能和人體偵測以外，還可以為屋內和屋外人士提供雙向對話，也能播放預設音訊或自訂錄製音訊作回應。DB60 特意設計了三種工作模式供用家選擇，分別是「自動」、「超省電」和「自訂」模式，用家能根據情況自己選擇模式以控制門鈴的耗電程度、錄影長度和解析度。產品支援 2.4 GHz WiFi，套裝包含的智能響鈴 (DS21)，除了作為門鈴響聲外，更可擴展家中 WiFi 覆蓋至門鈴使用，保證門鈴距離家內 WiFi 較遠也能流暢運作，讓用家隨時隨地都輕鬆監測門前狀況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DB60_lifestyle.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DB60_lifestyle-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DB60_lifestyle-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DB60_lifestyle-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DB60_lifestyle.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DB60Kit_DS21_lifestyle.jpg 1350w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2><strong>IMOU </strong><strong>無線錄影機，輕鬆集中管理及儲存鏡頭視頻</strong></h2><p>無線網路錄影機是能夠同時存取並記錄 IP 鏡頭視訊的裝置，IMOU 無線錄影機能快速配對其他 IMOU 鏡頭，實時解碼 1080P 錄影片段。用家可以接駁電視機或顯示屏作實時和長時間的錄影監控。錄影機具備 WiFi 功能，一經插 LAN 線即可釋放 WiFi 連接 IMOU 鏡頭，即使在沒有路由器的環境，也能和鏡頭保持穩定無線連接，並且可支援 16TB 硬碟，作長時間錄影。錄影機支援 Onvif 技術，可以連接支援該技術的非 IMOU 鏡頭，更有 4 頻道和 8 頻道兩種款式，顧客可根據鏡頭的數量作選擇。用戶們可以透過網頁瀏覽器或 IMOU APP 去控制鏡頭並進行實時監控，操作更加方便快捷。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-1280x897.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-768x538.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-1536x1077.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-03-16.19.23-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2><strong>B5 </strong><strong>智能燈泡，為家居帶來多元化燈光體驗</strong></h2><p>除了以保安為主的產品，IMOU 也有其他提升智能生活的家品。B5 智能燈泡提供高達 16,000,000 種顔色，並可隨意設定不同的燈光效果。B5 也能夠以語音控制開關和亮度，並且可以時間排程開關，更可以同時操控多個燈泡羣組，營造簡單方便又多元化的燈光效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle-694x361.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle-694x361.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle-1280x667.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle-768x400.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle-1536x800.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_lifestyle.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-317x580.png" alt="" width="317" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-317x580.png 317w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-492x900.png 492w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-768x1404.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-840x1536.png 840w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot-1121x2048.png 876w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/B5-CL1B-5-E27_product_shot.png 875w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 317px" /></a></p><p><strong>Rex 3D 5MP</strong></p><p>建議零售價：<strong>HK $578</strong></p><p><strong>Rex 2D 5MP </strong><br />
建議零售價：<strong>HK $458</strong></p><p><strong>Knight 8MP </strong></p><p>建議零售價：HK <strong>$1180</strong></p><p><strong>DB60 Kit    </strong></p><p>建議零售價：<strong>HK $1280</strong></p><p><strong>WiFi Recorder 8ch 1080p</strong></p><p>建議零售價：<strong>HK $990</strong></p><p><strong>B5 </strong></p><p>建議零售價：<strong>HK $118</strong></p><p>查詢：Imou 指定授權代理商 Winco (3619 8833)</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
